talic_en","text":"in the blackness of night:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(AZ, S:) the dim. is ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eu$ay~apN","text_ar":"عُشَيَّةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Az, TA.) In the saying"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jaA='a Ea$owapa","text_ar":"جَا=ءَ عَشْوَةَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ei$aA='F","text_ar":"عِشَا=ءً"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He came at nightfall"},{"kind":"text","text":"], it [is an adv. n. which] may not be used otherwise than thus: you may not say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maDato Ea$owapu","text_ar":"مَضَتْ عَشْوَةُ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlE$wp","text_ar":"العشوة"},{"kind":"text","text":"[app."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlEa$owapu","text_ar":"العَشْوَةُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"] as meaning"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlEa$aA='u","text_ar":"العَشَا=ءُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Algdwp","text_ar":"الغدوة"},{"kind":"text","text":"[app."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Algadowapu","text_ar":"الغَدْوَةُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"] as meaning"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlgadaA='u","text_ar":"الغَدَا=ءُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", is vulgar. (TA.)       -A2-  Also The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"venturing upon,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"embarking in, an affair that is not clear;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ei$owapN","text_ar":"عِشْوَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eu$owapN","text_ar":"عُشْوَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S, K:) one says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^awoTaA^otaniY Ea$owapF","text_ar":"اَوْطَاْتَنِى عَشْوَةً"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ei$owapF","text_ar":"عِشْوَةً"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eu$owapF","text_ar":"عُشْوَةً"},{"